{"tid":2139463,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"EVA 初號機焫雞　透明殼 + 可調溫度","createTime":"2020-08-04T09:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T13:04:21.000Z","uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"477e127861f683073d3c0c9fcd8aa45cb4cabe3b","tid":2139463,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"對於嘗試過焊接電子零件的朋友，對於焫雞（音「辣雞」，台灣稱為「電烙鐵」，即是小型焊接工具）不會陌生。近日有廠商 A.T.FIELD 推出三款撥盤式溫度控制的 EVA 焫雞，黃、紫和紅 3 種顏色分別代表著新世紀福音戰士的零號機、一號機和二號機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ATF-10011003_019-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FATF-10011003_019-1.jpg&h=de4f5ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ATF-10011003_016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FATF-10011003_016.jpg&h=30dbe466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3 種顏色的 EVA 焫雞把手都是透明的，使用者可以通過外殼看到焫雞內的零件和線路。撥動焊接器上的刻度盤，能夠將溫度調節到 200 至 500 度之間，使用者可以根據自己的工作，輕鬆調節最佳溫度，即使使用者將刻度盤設置在數字以外的刻度上，溫度也是準確的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ATF-10011003_018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FATF-10011003_018.jpg&h=2551f654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ATF-10011003_014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FATF-10011003_014.jpg&h=72fee31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEVA 焫雞的把手設置了 LED 數字燈，以指示溫度變化。當使用者把插頭插進插座時，溫度便會開始升高，LED 數字燈會長期亮起，代表焫雞正在加熱；直到上升至指定溫度，LED 數字燈便會閃動，代表焫雞已經預熱好可以使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ATF-10011003_005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FATF-10011003_005.jpg&h=a92ff7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ATF-10011003_009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FATF-10011003_009.jpg&h=fe80e289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n它可以快速地達到指定溫度，而且絕緣性極佳，適合焊接精密電子零件，例如 IC。而 EVA 焫雞的特點是從手柄到筆尖的長度很短，可以像拿著鉛筆一樣工作。<br />\n<br />\n同時，EVA 焫雞具有鎖定功能，可取下刻度盤防止溫度產生變化；經過重新設計以實現出色的導熱性尖端沒有使用鉛，因為鉛加熱後會對人體和環境產生負面影響。EVA 焫雞的售價為 8000 日元（約港幣 587 元）。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：KAKURI"},{"pid":"d8e7f94460f17510626bcce11e7516bf6b7acbf0","tid":2139463,"uid":54930,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:46:51.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁無恥仲出呢d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346ccd3a8705aff3ec21ee6debe89074acc955cf","tid":2139463,"uid":2477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"而家啲辣雞可以燒firmware 入去，有sensor detect 支雞係咪無人用可以cool down <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce02ecf8914a168f5813cdac28d894e2ae7d6cfd","tid":2139463,"uid":30084,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:53:07.000Z","msg":"甩左條線 會唔會暴走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094646d2e3df6413b1b60230b0f674b537dba206","tid":2139463,"uid":25743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"等睇hello kitty挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHellokitty：你敢挑戰我嘅地位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f457620f91f68cec938d8331c25e73df16a602","tid":2139463,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"求鳩其一樣野 <br />\n整個紫色再加少少瑩光綠就話係初號機呃錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b8eacbf8da08241d2bb5ed14db2091fb76da5f","tid":2139463,"uid":49004,"like":0,"